        p.head Simple game for your kids
        div.demo

            h2 🚀 Start
            p To start, run this code:
            pre.code
                span.blueb pip 
                span.orangeb install 
                span.greenb kanobu 
                br
                span.blueb kanobu
                
            p or you can start code without install:
            pre.code
                span.blueb python 
                span.greenb __main__.py
                
            h2 ⚙️ Options

            h3 --lang
            p For set default language. All languages placed in locale folder

            h3 --sqlite
            p For save to sqlite db

            h3 --version
            p Display kanobu version

